			h1.col-md-12 Our Leadership Team
			p.col-md-12 Our leadership team oversee our entire operation to make sure it's simple, effective and works for you!
			if teamMembers.length
				each teamMember in teamMembers
					.col
						img(src=teamMember.teamMemberImage)
						h2= teamMember.fullname
						p= teamMember.jobtitle
